high_descs: Turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot of water on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around, and face the stove.
Turn around, and walk to the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up the pot.
Turn around, and walk to the stove.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot of water on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the stove.
Pick up the dirty pot off of the front right burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the island and then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the dirty pot in the sink and turn on the water, after a few seconds turn the water off and take out the clean pot of water.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the stove.
Put the clean pot of water on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot of water on the back right burner of the stove.
